            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the rice is cooking, combine the <strong>achiote paste</strong>, <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> in a large bowl<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>achiote marinade</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>basa fillets</strong> to the <strong>achiote marinade</strong> and give everything a good mix up until the fish is completely covered</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
