    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>marinated fish</strong> and cook for 3-4 min on each side or until cooked through and slightly charred</p>",
